      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――怜の誕生日企画当日　早朝",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "yuvillaliving-00",
      "startTime": 1.7333334048
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "二人とも起きて！　もう朝よ",
      "startTime": 2.5666667382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "yuvillaliving-00",
      "startTime": 4.0333334048
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "yuvillaliving-00",
      "startTime": 5.8000002305
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "yuvillaliving-00",
      "startTime": 11.8000000715
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "うう～ん……まだ五時だよぉ……\n怜ちゃん早起きだね……撮影開始、九時からだよ……？",
      "startTime": 11.8000000715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "yuvillaliving-00",
      "startTime": 17.8892743032
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "早くないわよ。朝の準備してたらすぐなんだから\n誕生日企画はもう始まってるのよ？",
      "startTime": 22.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "朝の準備って……怜はもう完璧に整ってますけど……",
      "startTime": 25.6892743032,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "yuvillaliving-00",
      "startTime": 31.8226076365
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "私はこれからプランの最終チェックがあるの\nはい、着替えて",
      "startTime": 35.2226074775,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "yuvillaliving-00",
      "startTime": 37.5559409698
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、スタッフさんも起こした方がいいかしら？\n一緒に最後の打ち合わせとか――",
      "startTime": 41.4559408109,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "yuvillaliving-00",
      "startTime": 44.1226073822
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "スタッフさんがびっくりしちゃうよ……\n時間になったら迎えに来てもらえるから大丈夫だって",
      "startTime": 46.9691695584,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "yuvillaliving-00",
      "startTime": 51.230797585
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "怜は気が早いですわね……ふわぁ～……\n私、二度寝がしたいですわ",
      "startTime": 56.9641310137,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "yuvillaliving-00",
      "startTime": 60.5974642517
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "……いつもは起きるの遅いのに\n今日の怜ちゃんは気合い入ってるね……",
      "startTime": 63.1000041406,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "毎朝こうでしたら、遅刻もしませんのに……",
      "startTime": 66.1551564458,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "yuvillaliving-00",
      "startTime": 70.1884897791
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "……全部聞こえてるわよ\nあと、遅刻はしたことないから！",
      "startTime": 73.0218232078,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "yuvillaliving-00",
      "startTime": 76.2551564458
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "もう、くだらないこと言ってないで早く準備して\nあ、そろそろスタッフさんのこと迎えに行こうかしら",
      "startTime": 81.0884898744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "yuvillaliving-00",
      "startTime": 85.7884897791
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃん待ってぇ……さすがにもうちょっと\n後にしよう？　まだ起きて一分しか経ってないから……",
      "startTime": 89.4666758936,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.2814435088
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.2814435088
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣、すず、今日は思いっきり楽しむわよ！\nわ！　見て！　キャストさんがパフォーマンスしてる！",
      "startTime": 100.6981102708,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 14233.336385100003,
          "startTime": 114.9314466559
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.6981102708
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.0314435088
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、まずはエントランスで撮影よね！\nぬいぐるみも持ってるし！　写真、お願いしまーす",
      "startTime": 108.9647769375,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 15399.9964395,
          "startTime": 124.364773377
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.3647769375
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.7981213653
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.3981102708
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "この後はジェットコースター乗る？　あ！\nねえねえ、美味しそうなアイスのショップもあるわよ！",
      "startTime": 120.3314436041,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.964773377
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.2647900665
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃん、よっぽど楽しみだったんだろうね\nテーマパーク入ってから、ずーっと笑顔だよ",
      "startTime": 128.9333445948,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣達が頑張って笑顔を引き出さなきゃーとか\nしなくても大丈夫そうだね",
      "startTime": 135.3667084458,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。すでに怜の自然な笑顔が沢山出てますもの\n怜が楽しそうで何よりですわ",
      "startTime": 142.8658234044,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.8658411111
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "もー、二人とも置いてくわよ！　早く早くー！\nスタッフさんも！　こっちでーす！",
      "startTime": 151.3658234044,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9334.176595599985,
          "startTime": 160.7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.1991744445
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、分かったよー\nあ！　芽衣、あそこのポップコーン食べたいかも！",
      "startTime": 157.8333751125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.6993686604
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、ちょっと芽衣！？",
      "startTime": 161.6993686604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.5993778157
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "最新のアトラクションにも乗りたいけど……あ！\nあっちに限定グッズがあるみたい！　見てくるわね！",
      "startTime": 168.9660272842,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8733.333333299981,
          "startTime": 177.6993606175
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 172.932711149
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "すずはベンチに座って待ってて！\n終わったら戻ってくるから！",
      "startTime": 175.5660272842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 178.499370695
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
