      "text": "……あ、ごめん。さっき見た振りを私達のダンスに\n組み込めないかなって、考えてて",
      "startTime": 375.6033499961,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-night",
      "startTime": 378.5367005278
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03-rei022.m4a",
      "text": "私、帰ったらダンスの練習したい！\n今なら、振り付けを一杯生み出せる気がする！",
      "startTime": 382.2366833294,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-night",
      "startTime": 385.5367005278
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ。怜ちゃんは、本当にダンスが好きなんだね\nちょっとだけなら、芽衣も踊るよ！",
      "startTime": 390.1666819971,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-night",
      "startTime": 392.9480156352
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03-rei023.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、芽衣！\n三人でやってみたいダンスがあって――",
      "startTime": 394.9146651035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-night",
      "startTime": 397.6813489685
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "……え、三人って、私も！？\nふ、二人とも正気ですの！？",
      "startTime": 400.6146651035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-night",
      "startTime": 403.8480156352
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03-suz017.m4a",
      "text": "私は一日中撮影してくたくたですわ～！\n勘弁してくださいまし～！",
      "startTime": 408.0044531276,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03-rei024.m4a",
      "text": "（こんなに素敵な誕生日を過ごすのは、初めてだわ）\n（お仕事を忘れちゃうくらい浮かれるなんて）",
      "startTime": 418.1479984368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_51_03-rei025.m4a",
      "text": "（それに、憧れのダンサーさんを観れて、周りを笑顔に）\n（したり活力を与えるダンスの力を、改めて感じられた）",
      "startTime": 426.4809124081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
